{"change_summary":"Added optional `milestone_id` support to milestone task-run lineage, populated it on bead start/completion writes, backfilled and preserved it during lineage reads and `update_task_run` rewrites, and extended milestone-record tests to cover serialization, backward compatibility, legacy reads, bead queries, and outcome updates.","outstanding_risks":[],"steps":[{"description":"Added optional `milestone_id` to `TaskRunEntry` with serde defaults so lineage entries stay backward-compatible with existing NDJSON.","order":0,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Updated milestone task-run write and filesystem lineage paths so new start/completion records persist `milestone_id` and legacy entries retain or gain it during reads and outcome rewrites.","order":1,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Extended milestone lineage tests for milestone ID serialization, legacy backfill behavior, bead-run query visibility, and update flow preservation, then ran the requested validation commands.","order":2,"status":"completed"}],"validation_evidence":["`cargo fmt --all` completed successfully.","`cargo test --lib contexts::milestone_record` passed with 61 tests.","`cargo clippy -- -D warnings` completed successfully."]}